SC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kho%C3%A1-ti%E1%BB%83u-th%E1%BB%A5-s%E1%BB%AB-ch%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-x%C3%A1-b%E1%BA%AFc-qu%E1%BA%A3-l%C3%A2m-chi-m%E1%BA%A1n-hoang-u%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-ng%E1%BA%ADt-di-s%C3%A0ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-XM2SgmEcFWGaefrB5iIc-g">Khoá tiểu thụ sừ chước xá bắc quả lâm, chi mạn hoang uế, tịnh ngật di sàng kỳ 2 - 課小豎鋤斫舍北果林，枝蔓荒穢，淨訖移床三首其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/Ngu-m%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Ngu mỹ nhân kỳ 1 - 虞美人其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-x2jHtUhu4KZY4kl0A-lAIw">Lý Dục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thanh-ng%E1%BB%8Dc-%C3%A1n-Nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-1XqCFSRlIFFmW9NaFy9Dog">Thanh ngọc án - Nguyên tịch - 青玉案－元夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-WQkvak0bO6BDMarTsB2kng">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
